     2 \psi(2s) = \psi(s) + \psi\left(s+\frac{1}{2}\right) + 2 \log(2) \quad \stackrel{s=\frac{1}{2}}{\implies} \quad \psi\left(\frac{1}{2}\right) - \psi(1) = -2\ln(2) 
